# Document Lifecycle Rules

Document lifecycle state transitions must use dedicated endpoints.

Allowed lifecycle transitions:

publish
archive
restore
request-draft
merge-draft
delete

Lifecycle fields must NOT be modified via generic PATCH routes.

Forbidden in PATCH /documents/:id:

publishedAt
archivedAt
deletedAt

Lifecycle changes must use endpoints like:

POST /documents/:id/publish
POST /documents/:id/archive
POST /documents/:id/restore

These endpoints must call documentService lifecycle functions.